title: [Clunk's Weaponry]
description: Beneath a simple stone ceiling, a pair of crossed invar axes hangs on one of the speckled granite walls.  A slender silvery glaes display and some invar-braced shelves sit in opposite corners while a large granite boulder rests on a speckled granite floor.
Beneath a simple stone ceiling, a pair of crossed invar axes hangs on one of the plain wooden walls.  A plain wooden table sits in one corner while a worn rug rests on the granite floor.
